Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.97,0:13:18.95,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,人生一場虛空大夢 韶華白首不過轉瞬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.82,0:13:24.44,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,鳳僊花玉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.82,0:13:24.44,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,鳳僊花玉
